        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "The function's performance is efficient for small datasets but become a bottleneck in large-scale operations due to its iterative nature."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Consider using inline table-valued functions or incorporating the logic directly into queries for better performance in scenarios involving large datasets."
                }
              ]
